{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tutorial-js","path":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Objects/EditObjects/NodeAdjust/","webpackCompilationHash":"b56fc1f276773fcd7503","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><br>\n点平差功能可以实现相邻线的连接。点平差时对平差范围内（通过圈选确定）的全部节点进行平差计算，平差结果将产生一个新的节点，删除圈选的所有节点，在新节点处连接线对象。注意：连接仅是在节点处连接，并不是形成一个对象。</p>\n<p>如下图所示，选中相邻的四条线的端点（蓝色圆圈内的节点），对其进行平差操作，平差的结果是将四条线对象选中的节点全部删除，平差计算得到新节点，并将其与四条线上的其他节点分别相接，得到的结果如下图所示：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bb050f54ac1085ffdfe97d4510963e37/00397/NodeAdjust1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 256px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 76.95312500000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"NodeAdjust1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bb050f54ac1085ffdfe97d4510963e37/00397/NodeAdjust1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bb050f54ac1085ffdfe97d4510963e37/6a467/NodeAdjust1.png 210w,\n/static/bb050f54ac1085ffdfe97d4510963e37/00397/NodeAdjust1.png 256w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </th>\n<th>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/606489824e20265a2c65074726927877/00397/NodeAdjust2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 256px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 77.34374999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"NodeAdjust2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/606489824e20265a2c65074726927877/00397/NodeAdjust2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/606489824e20265a2c65074726927877/6a467/NodeAdjust2.png 210w,\n/static/606489824e20265a2c65074726927877/00397/NodeAdjust2.png 256w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>圈选参与操作的节点</td>\n<td>点平差结果</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"使用说明\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><img src=\"/read-56e09d9020b6fe36d2da63ae2fd275c5.gif\">使用说明</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>点平差功能适用于线图层和 CAD 图层。</li>\n<li>当圈选范围较大时，点平差操作对完全落入临时绘制的圆范围内的线对象不进行处理。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"操作步骤\"><a href=\"#%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><img src=\"/read-56e09d9020b6fe36d2da63ae2fd275c5.gif\">操作步骤</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>在图层可编辑状态下，在“ <strong>对象操作</strong> ”选项卡上的“ <strong>对象编辑</strong> ”组的 Gallery 控件中，单击“ <strong>点平差</strong> ”按钮，执行点平差操作。</li>\n<li>将鼠标移至地图窗口中，提示“鼠标圈选要平差的线的节点”。在地图窗口中绘制一个临时圆，使参与平差操作的节点恰好落入圆中。</li>\n<li>单击鼠标左键，对选中的节点进行平差操作。</li>\n<li>单击鼠标右键，即可取消当前操作。</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"点平差","next":null,"prev":null},"fields":{"path":"content\\tutorial\\DataProcessing\\Objects\\EditObjects\\NodeAdjust.zh.md","slug":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Objects/EditObjects/NodeAdjust/","langKey":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Objects/EditObjects/NodeAdjust/"}}}